{"tid":258282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雷霆17：灣仔破淫窟　拉俄羅斯台灣女","createTime":"2017-05-26T03:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T05:42:42.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c9b979498151838c584cf161f86f78c5334c064","tid":258282,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T03:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170526/photo/bkn-20170526000849282-0526_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170526111124\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170526%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170526000849282-0526_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170526111124&h=039a7020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n灣仔警區反三合會行動組聯同特別職務隊及入境處，根據線報並經深入調查後，於5月24日至25日，在灣仔區展開代號「雷霆17」及「虎尾」的反罪惡行動，打擊黑幫收入來源，警方突擊搜查區內多個住宅及商廈單位，搗破4個賣淫場所。行動中共拘捕30人，當中包括2男28女，其中2名本地男子(34及39歲)及一名本地女子(27歲)涉嫌「管理賣淫場所」及「協助及教唆管理賣淫場所」，其餘25名台灣籍女子(21至35歲)及2名俄羅斯籍女子(24及30歲)涉嫌「違反逗留條件」。<br />\n<br />\n警員在單位內檢獲大量毛巾、酒、潤滑劑及漱口水。所有被捕人士正被扣留調查。"},{"pid":"bdb66cba3626f6970e0e666bc0308ffd9de12c09","tid":258282,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:03:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6affc1b5e1cbdb13f4db18fdc956789dc573fa44","tid":258282,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86af83990041de34d13b28155c1e2717876ce956","tid":258282,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324c5b1291bbb5e5ed56ae04fc8bffa8f9ce8002","tid":258282,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:04:50.000Z","msg":"21歲 24歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a315d49e3c6fe93d384542a436de1d56624faeb","tid":258282,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-2